title: ‪Spyder Auto Installation: 1996-2001 Audi A4/S4 Sedan LED Tail Lights‬
description: This video will guide you through the process of installing a set of Spyder Auto LED Tail Lights on 1996-2001 Audi A4 and S4 sedan models. This tutorial will demonstrate how to fit the tail light onto any 96-01 A4 or S4 from start to finish. Available in your choice of clear, black/clear or red/clear finishes, these tail lights also feature a chrome-finish filler panel that you may remove and paint to match if desired.
tags: Spyder LED Tail Lights, Audi A4, S4, how to install, spyder lights, LED taillights
